ðŸ” Pass 3 (i = 2)
- Find minimum in `[25, 22, 64]` â†’ `22`
- Swap `25` and `22`  
âž¡ï¸ Result:  
```
[11, 12, 22, 25, 64]
```

---

ðŸ” Pass 4 (i = 3)
- Find minimum in `[25, 64]` â†’ `25`
- Already in correct position  
âž¡ï¸ Final Sorted Array:  
```
[11, 12, 22, 25, 64]
```

